parameters:
\N<Fubii>Yeah, of course. I've decided to live here from today. We're
becoming a couple, it's only natural, right?

\N<Fubii>Worried about money? Don't worry. I'm not going to be
smoldering away forever.

\N<Fubii>Eventually, I'll make a name for myself in Luda and earn a
lot. I'll make sure you can relax too, Auntie.

\N<Fubii>Then we'll leave this town together. Make sure you get Riia
ready for when that time comes, okay?

\N<Fubii>Even so... me, a father? It feels weird, but I guess I'll
have to get used to it, gotta be responsible.
